t: El spune El exista nedrept catre tu by întreba combina vostri oaie his! Multi(multe) popor combina their propietate trata each alt unfairly ala crede munci righteousness acestea exista puine. Afterwards David wondered daca el produce drept judecata! El medita noi proba him. El atunci implora his Domnitor forgiveness bowed jos regreta